sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as Bruger
    participant Widget as Live Activity / Dynamic Island
    participant Intent as App Intent
    participant Store as App Group Snapshot
    participant Supabase as Supabase anon client
    participant SQL as trackerlog + unique client_action_id
    participant App as iOS Tracker

    App->>Store: Gemmer TrackerLiveActivitySessionSnapshot
    App->>Widget: Starter/opdaterer ActivityKit state
    User->>Widget: Trykker reps/vægt/udført
    Widget->>Intent: Kører interaktiv App Intent
    Intent->>Store: Læser session snapshot og bearer token
    Intent->>Intent: Genererer client_action_id
    Intent->>Supabase: Insert trackerlog med anon key + user token
    Supabase->>SQL: RLS validerer auth.uid() og workout access
    SQL->>SQL: Unique index blokerer duplicate client_action_id
    SQL-->>Supabase: Insert success eller idempotent conflict
    Supabase-->>Intent: Resultat
    Intent->>Widget: Opdaterer projection/rest state
    App->>Supabase: Henter næste tracker-state ved foreground

